channel.title: Is there something missing?
channel.description:
Okay well here's the timeline trying to setup my first server
1. Downloaded project 16 2. Opened zip and clicked runserver 3. Opened No-ip DUC and checked the box on the left hand-side where the ip "pkscaped.no-ip.info" is placed... 4. Opened moparscape 5. It seems I have a router so I turned on hamachi. 6. I added pkscaped with the pass scaped 7. I clicked Start Server in Moparscape, then clicked OK, and then clicked enter, and then typed my pass, user, and ip which is "pkscaped.no-ip.info" 8. It says an error that it can't connect
Whats missing lol?????? can someone help?
When I type the IP 127.0.0.1 it works.. but when i type pkscaped.no-ip.info, it doesn't work...
